he same chat room this way users know who is available to talk all chat messages are archived and can be read by any site participant the chat room tool does not provide a way to chat privately by default all messages are visible to all participants however you can remove read access for a particular role and thereby for all participants with that role by modifying the chat room permissions printer friendly version printer friendly version
